{"text_id":109310,"tokens":["Title",":"," Elastic"," Scattering"," Theory"," and"," Transport"," in"," Graph","ene","\n\n","Abstract",":","\n","In"," this"," study",","," we"," address"," the"," challenge"," of"," understanding"," elastic"," scattering"," mechanisms"," and"," their"," impact"," on"," electronic"," transport"," in"," graphene","."," The"," unique"," electronic"," properties"," of"," graphene",","," characterized"," by"," its"," linear"," energy"," dispersion"," and"," high"," carrier"," mobility",","," make"," it"," a"," promising"," material"," for"," next","-","generation"," electronic"," devices","."," However",","," the"," presence"," of"," impurities"," and"," defects"," can"," significantly"," affect"," its"," transport"," properties","."," Our"," research"," is"," motivated"," by"," the"," need"," to"," develop"," a"," comprehensive"," theoretical"," framework"," that"," accurately"," describes"," elastic"," scattering"," processes"," in"," graphene","."," We"," employ"," a"," combination"," of"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," techniques"," to"," investigate"," the"," scattering"," of"," charge"," carriers"," by"," various"," types"," of"," impurities",","," including"," point"," defects"," and"," charged"," impurities","."," Our"," results"," reveal"," that"," the"," nature"," and"," concentration"," of"," impurities"," play"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," determining"," the"," transport"," characteristics"," of"," graphene","."," We"," find"," that"," short","-","range"," scatter","ers"," predominantly"," influence"," low","-","energy"," carriers",","," while"," long","-","range"," scatter","ers"," affect"," high","-","energy"," carriers","."," Additionally",","," we"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," scattering"," rate"," is"," highly"," anisotropic",","," reflecting"," the"," underlying"," symmetry"," of"," the"," graphene"," lattice","."," These"," findings"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," into"," the"," design"," and"," optimization"," of"," graphene","-","based"," electronic"," devices",","," highlighting"," the"," importance"," of"," controlling"," impurity"," types"," and"," concentrations"," to"," achieve"," desired"," transport"," properties","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4o","label":1}